# Development Standards

- Code Nodes: Always try { } catch { console.error(); throw; } return {success: true, data}.
- Workflows: Create inactive, name as per blueprint, log ID; export JSON via claude-code-mcp.
- Retries: MAX_RETRIES=3, exponential backoff.
- Tests: Show outputs, e.g., "Test input: {}, Output: {}"; generate scripts via claude-code-mcp if testsprite fails (announce switch).
- Airtable: Retry on fail, batch 50; generate CSV schemas via claude-code-mcp as fallback.
- SMS: Max 135 chars content, addOptOutLanguage=true.
- Costs: Check before API, log after.
- Always announce MCP fallbacks before switching to claude-code-mcp.